# Learn Project 🎓💬  
A lightweight, AI-integrated learning management platform built with PHP, MySQL, and ChatGPT API

## 🔧 Overview
This project aims to provide a scalable, modular, and user-friendly web application that facilitates online learning. With features such as point logging, progress tracking, and ChatGPT-powered support, the platform is ideal for students and small institutions seeking an intuitive self-learning environment.

## 🧠 Key Features
- 🔐 **User Authentication** – Secure login/register with session control.
- 📊 **Learning Tracker** – Log study sessions and monitor your academic progress.
- 🤖 **ChatGPT AI Assistant** – Built-in conversational AI support using the OpenAI API.
- 📁 **Modular MVC Architecture** – Clean code organization for maintainability and scalability.
- 🔒 **Security** – Uses prepared statements to prevent SQL injection and `.env` for sensitive credentials.

## 📂 Project Structure (MVC)
/app
/controllers → Handles user and API requests
/models → Business logic and database operations
/views → HTML views and frontend templates
/public
/css → Stylesheets
/js → Frontend JS (chatbox, fetch API)
index.php → Routing entry point
/config
config.php → DB config using environment variables
.env → Hidden credentials file
/gpt.api → ChatGPT backend handler (via OpenAI API)

