## 🤝 Dependencies
- [PHP 8.x](https://www.php.net/)
- [MySQL](https://www.mysql.com/)
- [Composer](https://getcomposer.org/) (for dotenv)
- [OpenAI PHP SDK](https://github.com/openai/openai-php)
- [XAMPP](https://www.apachefriends.org/) (for local development)

## 🚀 Setup Instructions

1. **Clone the repository**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/fitiotan/learn-project.git
cd learn-project
Install dependencies

