composer install
Set up .env

env
Copy
Edit
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_NAME=learn_project
DB_USER=root
DB_PASS=
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here
Import the database
Import the included SQL file into your MySQL database using phpMyAdmin or MySQL CLI.

Run on XAMPP
Place the project in your XAMPP htdocs/ folder and start Apache & MySQL via the XAMPP Control Panel.

💬 ChatGPT Integration
The chatbot is implemented using gpt.php, which:

Takes input from a frontend chatbox

Sends a POST request to the OpenAI API

Returns a formatted response to the user interface

